headline: Expect more fintech companies to go public in 2026: VC investor
summary: Klarna (KLAR) and eToro (ETOR) are just a couple of fintech names that went public this year. QED Investors co-founder and managing partner and Capital One co-founder Nigel Morris expects even more to go public next year and into 2027. Find out why in the video above. headline: Three Stocks That Could Be Undervalued By Market Estimates In December 2025
summary: As we enter December 2025, the U.S. stock market presents a mixed picture with major indices like the Dow and S&P 500 hovering near all-time highs while investors closely monitor upcoming inflation data that could influence Federal Reserve decisions on interest rates.
